      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEWILLDOUS (2) has finished off strongly from the back of the pack in both runs this time in work. This is a much easier assignment today and he's a winner over this track and trip today. Can sit a touch closer in the run than he has done his past couple and he can extend his unbeaten third-up record. CANTILEVER (4) was far too good over the mile here last time out, bolting in by 2.5L at this track. He was solid from the front over this track and trip two runs back and he has enough speed to sit on the speed from the inside alley. Will be tough to run down. CATERAN (6) flew home from the back of the pack to be 2.6L off the winner last time out after a good win here two back. Needs some luck from the draw but is good enough if the gaps come. BENTLEY BEAU (7) can improve third-up and with a slight gear change. TRADED CROWN (8) won't be far away fresh from the inside draw.",
